166
00:16:26.820 --> 00:16:28.529
<font color="#fecb00">Either-- You know what I mean.</font>

167
00:16:28.530 --> 00:16:30.865
<font color="#fecb00">We need money to hunt Titans.</font>

168
00:16:30.866 --> 00:16:34.578
<font color="#fecb00">but we need to prove Titans exist
