169
00:16:36.246 --> 00:16:39.416
<font color="#fecb00">Look. for the good of Monarch.
something's gotta give.</font>

170
00:16:48.467 --> 00:16:52.803
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">- It's in the middle of the Sahara.
- Not the middle-middle. More like the--</font>

171
00:16:52.804 --> 00:16:55.056
<font color="#fecb00">- North-middle.
- Yeah. of a giant desert.</font>

172
00:16:55.057 --> 00:16:56.307
<font color="#fecb00">So?</font>

173
00:16:56.308 --> 00:16:57.851
<font color="#fecb00">We got Dad's map.</font>

174
00:16:59.144 --> 00:17:00.895
<font color="#fecb00">Nut up and pack a sun hat.</font>

175
00:17:00.896 --> 00:17:02.356
<font color="#fecb00">How are we even gonna get there?</font>

176
00:17:03.357 --> 00:17:04.566
<font color="#fecb00">Get where?</font>

177
00:17:06.108 --> 00:17:07.193
<font color="#fecb00">- Mom?
- Shit.</font>

178
00:17:07.194 --> 00:17:08.403
<font color="#fecb00">Colonel.</font>

179
00:17:08.987 --> 00:17:11.280
<font color="#fecb00">- Mom?
- Cate. your mom is fine.</font>

180
00:17:11.281 --> 00:17:13.406
<font color="#fecb00">She's out throwing pots
