183
00:17:17.621 --> 00:17:20.748
<font color="#fecb00">A little help from the outside.
sometimes from the inside.</font>

184
00:17:20.749 --> 00:17:21.958
<font color="#fecb00">What's she doing here?</font>

185
00:17:21.959 --> 00:17:25.294
<font color="#fecb00">Well. Michelle's dancing
on the side of the angels now.</font>

186
00:17:25.295 --> 00:17:26.964
<font color="#fecb00">Pretty respectable dancer too.</font>

187
00:17:27.881 --> 00:17:29.216
<font color="#fecb00">We can use her help.</font>

188
00:17:29.800 --> 00:17:31.259
<font color="#fecb00">Something's coming.</font>

189
00:17:31.260 --> 00:17:34.304
<font color="#fecb00">G-Day times a hundred.</font>

190
00:17:34.888 --> 00:17:36.807
<font color="#fecb00">Maybe times a thousand.</font>

191
00:17:37.391 --> 00:17:39.475
<font color="#fecb00">I think your father's trying to stop
