192
00:17:39.476 --> 00:17:41.645
<font color="#fecb00">and I got a pretty good idea
how he's gonna do it.</font>

193
00:17:42.437 --> 00:17:44.314
<font color="#fecb00">Only way to know for sure is to find him.</font>

