<font color="#fecb00">- This is it.
- You sure?</font>

390
00:31:01.028 --> 00:31:04.906
<font color="#fecb00">Well. I'm sure this is
the spot on the map.</font>

391
00:31:04.907 --> 00:31:07.910
<font color="#fecb00">but what that means exactly
only your dad can tell us.</font>

392
00:31:09.453 --> 00:31:11.413
<font color="#fecb00">But yeah.</font>

393
00:31:12.080 --> 00:31:14.958
<font color="#fecb00">I think it's just over this ridge.</font>

394
00:31:44.154 --> 00:31:45.155
<font color="#fecb00">There.</font>

395
00:31:46.073 --> 00:31:47.658
<font color="#fecb00">- Where?
- You see? There.</font>

396
00:31:51.286 --> 00:31:52.453
<font color="#fecb00">Is that--</font>

397
00:31:52.454 --> 00:31:54.122
<font color="#fecb00">Well. I'll be damned.</font>

398
00:32:15.769 --> 00:32:16.770
<font color="#fecb00">He's alive.</font>

399
00:32:18.146 --> 00:32:22.693
<font color="#fecb00">Dad! Over here. Dad!</font>

400
00:32:23.735 --> 00:32:26.821
<font color="#fecb00">- Dad!
- Up here!</font>

401
00:32:26.822 --> 00:32:28.282
<font color="#fecb00">Dad!</font>

402
00:32:33.787 --> 00:32:35.038
<font color="#fecb00">Dad!</font>

403
00:33:22.211 --> 00:33:24.170
<font color="#fecb00">Reading's flatter
than hammered shit. Suzuki.</font>

404
00:33:24.171 --> 00:33:27.091
<font color="#fecb00">I thought you said turning this thing on
was like ringing the dinner bell.</font>

405
00:33:27.716 --> 00:33:28.925
<font color="#fecb00">My father used to say.</font>

406
00:33:28.926 --> 00:33:32.346
<font color="#fecb00">"There is a reason
they call it fishing. not catching."</font>

407
00:33:34.264 --> 00:33:35.766
<font color="#fecb00">My pop said the same thing.</font>

408
00:33:42.481 --> 00:33:44.107
<font color="#fecb00">Have you ever seen one?</font>

409
00:33:44.691 --> 00:33:45.692
<font color="#fecb00">For certain?</font>

410
00:33:46.777 --> 00:33:48.445
<font color="#fecb00">A Titan.</font>

411
00:33:49.821 --> 00:33:52.199
<font color="#fecb00">Yes. we have.</font>

412
00:33:56.662 --> 00:33:57.829
<font color="#fecb00">They are terrifying.</font>

413
00:34:00.624 --> 00:34:01.625
<font color="#fecb00">Good!</font>

414
00:34:03.252 --> 00:34:06.213
<font color="#fecb00">Miracles should be terrifying.</font>

415
00:34:06.839 --> 00:34:07.965
<font color="#fecb00">Don't you think?</font>

416
00:34:10.801 --> 00:34:12.678
<font color="#fecb00">Guys. something's coming.</font>

417
00:34:13.846 --> 00:34:15.556
<font color="#fecb00">No. it ain't coming from the water.</font>

418
00:34:26.859 --> 00:34:29.151
<font color="#fecb00">Lee! Didn't think you were gonna
make the party.</font>

419
00:34:29.152 --> 00:34:31.780
<font color="#fecb00">- Wouldn't miss it.
- How'd the serenade go with the bigwigs?</font>

420
00:34:32.364 --> 00:34:34.323
<font color="#fecb00">Wait. I thought that was today.</font>

421
00:34:34.324 --> 00:34:36.493
<font color="#fecb00">It is today.</font>

422
00:34:39.621 --> 00:34:42.999
<font color="#fecb00">Hey. this is Dr. Suzuki</font>

423
00:34:43.000 --> 00:34:45.084
<font color="#fecb00">and he made a--</font>

424
00:34:45.085 --> 00:34:47.086
<font color="#fecb00">- A gamma radiation simulator.
- Yeah.</font>

425
00:34:47.087 --> 00:34:50.006
<font color="#fecb00">That's great.
I can't wait to hear all about it.</font>

426
00:34:50.007 --> 00:34:53.009
<font color="#fecb00">It's a device that
actually simulates gamma radiation...</font>

427
00:34:53.010 --> 00:34:55.218
<font color="#fecb00">- Hey. Zook...
- ...and it's not just--</font>

428
00:34:55.219 --> 00:34:57.500
<font color="#fecb00">...you know the only thing worse
than being a third wheel?</font>

429
00:34:58.015 --> 00:34:59.600
<font color="#fecb00">Being a fourth. Let's walk.</font>

430
00:35:00.726 --> 00:35:03.395
<font color="#fecb00">But four wheels are intrinsically stable.</font>

431
00:35:04.188 --> 00:35:06.815
<font color="#fecb00">That's why a car has four wheels. Cars...</font>

432
00:35:22.247 --> 00:35:25.334
<font color="#fecb00">Now. wait a minute.
I think he's waving us off.</font>

433
00:35:26.418 --> 00:35:28.127
<font color="#fecb00">- Why? What's going on?
- Oh. no.</font>

434
00:35:28.128 --> 00:35:30.088
<font color="#fecb00">- What is he doing?
- No.</font>

435
00:35:37.888 --> 00:35:39.972
<font color="#fecb00">We gotta get out of here!
Come on. we gotta move! Now!</font>

436
00:35:39.973 --> 00:35:42.225
<font color="#fecb00">Now! Move! We need to go now!</font>

437
00:35:42.226 --> 00:35:43.393
<font color="#fecb00">Kentaro. we gotta go!</font>

438
00:35:44.269 --> 00:35:45.604
<font color="#fecb00">We gotta go now!</font>

439
00:35:58.450 --> 00:36:00.494
<font color="#fecb00">There they are! That's them.</font>

440
00:36:07.042 --> 00:36:08.460
<font color="#fecb00">Columbo. baby!</font>

441
00:36:09.211 --> 00:36:10.671
<font color="#fecb00">Take us down.</font>

442
00:36:33.402 --> 00:36:34.903
<font color="#fecb00">You weren't supposed to come.</font>

443
00:36:38.574 --> 00:36:41.493
<font color="#fecb00">My place is here with you. Kei.</font>

444
00:36:43.453 --> 00:36:44.705
<font color="#fecb00">- You need--
- What?</font>

445
00:36:46.248 --> 00:36:47.332
<font color="#fecb00">Your protection?</font>

446
00:36:48.125 --> 00:36:49.125
<font color="#fecb00">That's my job.</font>

447
00:36:49.126 --> 00:36:51.378
<font color="#fecb00">No. your job is to protect Monarch.</font>

448
00:36:52.004 --> 00:36:55.174
<font color="#fecb00">Without you. there is no Monarch.</font>

449
00:36:58.844 --> 00:37:00.554
<font color="#fecb00">Tell me that's not why you're here.</font>

450
00:37:01.471 --> 00:37:02.472
<font color="#fecb00">For me.</font>

451
00:37:22.326 --> 00:37:23.993
<font color="#fecb00">You know we can't do this.</font>

452
00:37:23.994 --> 00:37:25.078
<font color="#fecb00">We can try.</font>

453
00:37:28.832 --> 00:37:30.875
<font color="#fecb00">How long before either of us
makes a decision</font>

454
00:37:30.876 --> 00:37:32.168
<font color="#fecb00">based on what we want to do</font>

455
00:37:32.169 --> 00:37:33.670
<font color="#fecb00">instead of what Monarch needs?</font>

456
00:37:34.379 --> 00:37:35.881
<font color="#fecb00">You don't trust me.</font>

457
00:37:42.763 --> 00:37:44.181
<font color="#fecb00">I don't trust either of us.</font>

458
00:37:50.854 --> 00:37:53.899
<font color="#fecb00">If we can't put the greater good
before our own desires.</font>

459
00:37:55.400 --> 00:37:56.735
<font color="#fecb00">we risk losing everything.</font>

460
00:37:57.986 --> 00:37:59.196
<font color="#fecb00">I don't care.</font>

461
00:38:11.166 --> 00:38:14.002
<font color="#fecb00">Yes. you do.</font>

462
00:38:25.138 --> 00:38:26.139
<font color="#fecb00">It stopped.</font>

463
00:38:27.182 --> 00:38:28.183
<font color="#fecb00">What?</font>

464
00:38:29.476 --> 00:38:30.477
<font color="#fecb00">The device.</font>

465
00:38:31.478 --> 00:38:32.604
<font color="#fecb00">It stopped.</font>

466
00:38:37.276 --> 00:38:38.277
<font color="#fecb00">Where is it?</font>

467
00:38:52.624 --> 00:38:53.709
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my God.</font>

468
00:39:23.906 --> 00:39:24.907
<font color="#fecb00">We didn't kill it.</font>

469
00:39:26.408 --> 00:39:28.368
<font color="#fecb00">Jesus Christ. we didn't kill it.</font>

470
00:39:35.667 --> 00:39:37.002
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Wait. don't land.</i></font>

471
00:39:45.677 --> 00:39:47.387
<font color="#fecb00"><i>The hell is that?</i></font>

472
00:40:17.167 --> 00:40:18.418
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my God.</font>

473
00:41:50.344 --> 00:41:53.262
<font color="#fecb00">Get us out of here! Pull up! Hey! Pull up!</font>

474
00:41:53.263 --> 00:41:54.597
<font color="#fecb00">Pull up!</font>

475
00:41:54.598 --> 00:41:55.849
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Brace for impact!</i></font>

476
00:42:30.676 --> 00:42:31.802
<font color="#fecb00">Did you see?</font>

477
00:42:33.679 --> 00:42:34.680
<font color="#fecb00">He saw me.</font>

478
00:42:36.098 --> 00:42:37.099
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. he did.</font>

479
00:42:45.524 --> 00:42:47.859
<font color="#fecb00">- We cannot keep them in the dark.
- Why not?</font>

480
00:42:47.860 --> 00:42:49.652
<font color="#fecb00">Look. I know how you feel about Puckett...</font>

481
00:42:49.653 --> 00:42:51.904
<font color="#fecb00">- Puckett.
- ...but this changes everything.</font>

482
00:42:51.905 --> 00:42:53.281
<font color="#fecb00">I don't agree.</font>

483
00:42:53.282 --> 00:42:55.950
<font color="#fecb00">The most powerful weapon
this country's ever created</font>

484
00:42:55.951 --> 00:42:59.161
<font color="#fecb00">could not bring that thing down.
so we can't keep that to ourselves.</font>

485
00:42:59.162 --> 00:43:00.830
<font color="#fecb00">So we tell them and then what?</font>

486
00:43:00.831 --> 00:43:02.164
<font color="#fecb00">They build an even bigger weapon</font>

487
00:43:02.165 --> 00:43:03.083
<font color="#fecb00">- and try again.
- Kei...</font>

488
00:43:03.084 --> 00:43:05.293
<font color="#fecb00">And if that doesn't work.
an even bigger one.</font>

489
00:43:05.294 --> 00:43:07.086
<font color="#fecb00">And if they can't find Godzilla.</font>

490
00:43:07.087 --> 00:43:09.173
<font color="#fecb00">maybe then they'll find
somebody else to use it on.</font>

491
00:43:13.510 --> 00:43:15.803
<font color="#fecb00">I wasn't supposed to
go after you two.</font>

492
00:43:15.804 --> 00:43:18.556
<font color="#fecb00">And I certainly wasn't supposed to
come back empty-handed.</font>

493
00:43:18.557 --> 00:43:20.975
<font color="#fecb00">so I need something-- We need something.</font>

494
00:43:20.976 --> 00:43:22.935
<font color="#fecb00">anything that I can put
in front of Puckett</font>

495
00:43:22.936 --> 00:43:24.813
<font color="#fecb00">so we can get our asses
out of the doghouse.</font>

496
00:43:31.778 --> 00:43:32.779
<font color="#fecb00">All right.</font>

497
00:43:35.782 --> 00:43:36.867
<font color="#fecb00">All right.</font>

498
00:43:37.576 --> 00:43:39.578
<font color="#fecb00">So let's get our shit together. yeah?</font>

499
00:43:40.454 --> 00:43:42.080
<font color="#fecb00">I'll try and go sell this to Puckett.</font>

500
00:43:46.251 --> 00:43:48.962
<font color="#fecb00">Gentlemen. Doctor.</font>

501
00:43:51.548 --> 00:43:54.592
<font color="#fecb00">Just going over
some of your field reports.</font>

502
00:43:54.593 --> 00:43:57.094
<font color="#fecb00">Some wild stuff in here.</font>

503
00:43:57.095 --> 00:43:58.805
<font color="#fecb00">Who the-- What's going on?</font>

504
00:43:59.389 --> 00:44:02.518
<font color="#fecb00">In the Navy.
we call it "change of command."</font>

505
00:44:04.144 --> 00:44:07.230
<font color="#fecb00">During Captain Shaw's
unauthorized absence.</font>

506
00:44:07.231 --> 00:44:09.941
<font color="#fecb00">General Puckett handed
operational command and control</font>

507
00:44:09.942 --> 00:44:12.528
<font color="#fecb00">of Project Monarch to me.</font>

508
00:44:13.820 --> 00:44:17.406
<font color="#fecb00">I'll expect a full report and accounting
of your little field trip</font>

509
00:44:17.407 --> 00:44:20.202
<font color="#fecb00">on my desk by end of day.</font>

510
00:44:24.748 --> 00:44:25.916
<font color="#fecb00">What have you done?</font>

511
00:44:37.177 --> 00:44:38.303
<font color="#fecb00">Did you find anyone?</font>

512
00:44:39.388 --> 00:44:42.266
<font color="#fecb00">No one survived the crash.
and we're running out of time.</font>

513
00:44:43.892 --> 00:44:46.018
<font color="#fecb00">We need to find out
where Godzilla is going</font>

514
00:44:46.019 --> 00:44:49.355
<font color="#fecb00">before Monarch does.
so we need to move now.</font>

515
00:44:49.356 --> 00:44:51.899
<font color="#fecb00">- This is gonna lead us to him.
- That map belongs to us.</font>

516
00:44:51.900 --> 00:44:53.901
<font color="#fecb00">No. this map stays with me.</font>

517
00:44:53.902 --> 00:44:55.570
<font color="#fecb00">So we chase Godzilla. then what?</font>

518
00:44:55.571 --> 00:44:58.406
<font color="#fecb00">More people die? We can't stop him.</font>

519
00:44:58.407 --> 00:44:59.491
<font color="#fecb00">Stop him?</font>

520
00:45:01.285 --> 00:45:04.787
<font color="#fecb00">Jesus. Cate. I'm trying to help him.</font>

521
00:45:04.788 --> 00:45:06.790
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my God. You're insane.</font>

522
00:45:09.293 --> 00:45:11.253
<font color="#fecb00">What I am is done debating.</font>

523
00:45:11.795 --> 00:45:14.463
<font color="#fecb00">But if you come with me.
you'll know everything.</font>

524
00:45:14.464 --> 00:45:16.383
<font color="#fecb00">- I promise you.
- No.</font>

525
00:45:17.384 --> 00:45:19.970
<font color="#fecb00">The only place we're going
is after our father.</font>

526
00:45:21.305 --> 00:45:22.514
<font color="#fecb00">I'm out.</font>

527
00:45:31.356 --> 00:45:32.482
<font color="#fecb00">I'm going with them.</font>

528
00:45:36.486 --> 00:45:38.279
<font color="#fecb00">I'll leave you plenty of water and food.</font>

529
00:45:38.280 --> 00:45:42.242
<font color="#fecb00">You won't need it 'cause civilization
is just ten klicks that way.</font>

530
00:45:45.537 --> 00:45:47.831
<font color="#fecb00">You go now.
you'll be there long before dinner.</font>

531
00:45:49.333 --> 00:45:50.584
<font color="#fecb00">Allons-y.</font>

532
00:46:15.067 --> 00:46:16.902
<font color="#fecb00">Do you think he was waving us away?</font>

533
00:46:17.611 --> 00:46:18.612
<font color="#fecb00">I don't know.</font>

534
00:46:21.448 --> 00:46:22.449
<font color="#fecb00">He just took off.</font>

535
00:46:25.577 --> 00:46:27.204
<font color="#fecb00">Maybe he was running from Godzilla.</font>

536
00:46:28.372 --> 00:46:30.791
<font color="#fecb00">Or trying to lure him. you know.
away from us.</font>

537
00:46:32.584 --> 00:46:34.711
<font color="#fecb00">At least we know he made it this far.</font>

538
00:46:35.671 --> 00:46:36.672
<font color="#fecb00">And so did we.</font>

539
00:46:38.173 --> 00:46:39.508
<font color="#fecb00">He's alive.</font>

540
00:46:40.050 --> 00:46:41.051
<font color="#fecb00">So we keep looking.</font>

541
00:46:43.762 --> 00:46:45.680
<font color="#fecb00">How many klicks have we gone?</font>

542
00:46:45.681 --> 00:46:46.765
<font color="#fecb00">No idea.</font>

543
00:46:49.184 --> 00:46:50.686
<font color="#fecb00">How are we gonna go from here?</font>

544
00:46:51.353 --> 00:46:52.938
<font color="#fecb00">We don't have any money or phones.</font>

545
00:46:53.438 --> 00:46:54.814
<font color="#fecb00">How are we going to find Dad
without the map?</font>

546
00:46:54.815 --> 00:46:57.526
<font color="#fecb00">Well. someone always seems to have
a backup of her backups.</font>

547
00:46:58.277 --> 00:46:59.917
<font color="#fecb00">You wouldn't let us down. would you. May?</font>

548
00:47:06.869 --> 00:47:07.869
<font color="#fecb00">It was a joke.</font>

549
00:47:07.870 --> 00:47:11.164
<font color="#fecb00">No. I can't do this anymore.
This is my fault.</font>

550
00:47:12.249 --> 00:47:15.752
<font color="#fecb00">- What do you mean?
- Seriously. No. I sold you out.</font>

551
00:47:18.672 --> 00:47:21.884
<font color="#fecb00">- What?
- Just hear me out. okay?</font>

552
00:47:23.385 --> 00:47:25.846
<font color="#fecb00">A couple of years ago.
I pissed some people off</font>

553
00:47:26.471 --> 00:47:29.682
<font color="#fecb00">and I let some people down.
and so I had to run.</font>

554
00:47:29.683 --> 00:47:31.351
<font color="#fecb00">And then I ran to Japan</font>

555
00:47:32.019 --> 00:47:35.771
<font color="#fecb00">and I lied about my life and my name.
who I was.</font>

556
00:47:35.772 --> 00:47:39.817
<font color="#fecb00">And I was living nice and quiet
until Monarch figured me out</font>

557
00:47:39.818 --> 00:47:41.068
<font color="#fecb00">when they picked us up.</font>

558
00:47:41.069 --> 00:47:42.278
<font color="#fecb00">They left a deal on the table.</font>

559
00:47:42.279 --> 00:47:44.363
<font color="#fecb00">and they said that if I told them
where we were.</font>

560
00:47:44.364 --> 00:47:46.532
<font color="#fecb00">I could go home
and I could get my life back</font>

561
00:47:46.533 --> 00:47:47.951
<font color="#fecb00">and I could be with my family.</font>

562
00:47:48.702 --> 00:47:53.707
<font color="#fecb00">And so. yes. I sold us out.
and I'm the reason that they found us.</font>

563
00:47:55.292 --> 00:47:57.084
<font color="#fecb00">"The only way out is through."</font>

564
00:47:57.085 --> 00:48:00.171
<font color="#fecb00">- Look. I have money.
- I don't want your goddamn money.</font>

565
00:48:00.172 --> 00:48:01.923
<font color="#fecb00">Listen. I have a lot of money.</font>

566
00:48:01.924 --> 00:48:04.050
<font color="#fecb00">And I never touched it because
the wrong people could find me.</font>

567
00:48:04.051 --> 00:48:05.676
<font color="#fecb00">But I don't care anymore.
It doesn't matter.</font>

568
00:48:05.677 --> 00:48:07.345
<font color="#fecb00">I can get us wherever you wanna go.</font>

569
00:48:07.346 --> 00:48:08.430
<font color="#fecb00">Go to hell.</font>

570
00:48:11.058 --> 00:48:12.309
<font color="#fecb00">Cate. I'm sorry.</font>

571
00:48:13.894 --> 00:48:15.020
<font color="#fecb00">Cate.</font>
